feed.title: Sump Pump Monitor
feed.description: Arduino Uno is connected to an Wifly shield.  I am using an MPX5010 pressure sensor connected to a tube into sump pit . The project also has 2 seven segment displays showing the water height. The project is monitoring my sump pit so that I can check on the water height from Hubcape.  I get a Prowl notification when the water level exceeds 12".  I set up a trigger that sends me an SMS from my Twilio account when the water level is high. Flooding is a concern to me because I have a high water table.
